docs {
  # Get All Health Tips

  Retrieves a random selection of health tips from the health.gov API.

  ## Query Parameters

  - `limit` (number, optional): Number of health tips to retrieve. Defaults to 6 if not provided.
    - Must be greater than 0
    - Example: `?limit=10` returns 10 random health tips

  ## Success Response (200 OK)

  ```json
  {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Health tips retrieved successfully",
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "350",
        "title": "Get Tested for Chlamydia and Gonorrhea",
        "imageUrl": "https://odphp.health.gov/sites/default/files/2024-01/Get_Tested_Chlamydia_Gonorrhea.jpg",
        "imageAlt": "A man and woman smiling"
      },
      {
        "id": "514",
        "title": "Get Screened for Breast Cancer",
        "imageUrl": "https://odphp.health.gov/sites/default/files/...",
        "imageAlt": "Woman at doctor's office"
      }
    ]
  }
  ```

  Note: The response excludes `lastUpdated` and `mainContent` fields for this endpoint.

  ## Error Response (422 Validation Error)

  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Validation Error: ✖ Limit must be a number → at limit",
    "errors": {
      "limit": ["Limit must be a number"]
    }
  }
  ```

  Or if limit is invalid:

  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Validation Error: ✖ Limit must be greater than 0 → at limit",
    "errors": {
      "limit": ["Limit must be greater than 0"]
    }
  }
  ```
}
